summary(lm2)$r.squared
    </pre>
    
    <h2>Question 5</h2>
    <p>The piecewise model is considered adequate when the coefficients of x¬≤ are low. For example, in Q3, they are x6 and x7 and are of the order 10‚Åª‚Å¥.</p>
    
    <h2>Question 6</h2>
